384
00:26:49,524 --> 00:26:51,552
Wow! It's mating!

385
00:26:53,317 --> 00:26:56,325
You never just walk past it, do you?

386
00:26:58,963 --> 00:27:00,931
Oh! It's a cow!

387
00:27:05,276 --> 00:27:06,760
If he bumps into you,

388
00:27:06,845 --> 00:27:08,896
