969
01:03:08,881 --> 01:03:09,707
<i>Should I...</i>

970
01:03:09,816 --> 01:03:12,301
<i>tell him that I'm going to become a human?</i>

971
01:03:12,408 --> 01:03:13,768
<i>Even if you become a human,</i>

972
